  "chapter": {
    "number": 4,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "The Day of the LORD"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 1,
        "content": [
          "“For behold, the day is coming, burning like a furnace, when all the arrogant and every evildoer will be stubble; the day is coming when I will set them ablaze,” says the LORD of Hosts. “Not a root or branch will be left to them.”"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 2,
        "content": [
          "“But for you who fear My name, the sun of righteousness will rise with healing in its wings,",
          {
            "noteId": 3608
          },
          "and you will go out and leap like calves from the stall."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 3,
        "content": [
          "Then you will trample the wicked, for they will be ashes under the soles of your feet on the day I am preparing,” says the LORD of Hosts."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 4,
        "content": [
          "“Remember the law of My servant Moses, the statutes and ordinances I commanded him for all Israel at Horeb.",
          {
            "noteId": 3609
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 5,
        "content": [
          "Behold, I will send you Elijah the prophet before the coming of the great and awesome",
          {
            "noteId": 3610
          },
          "Day of the LORD."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 6,
        "content": [
          "And he will turn the hearts of the fathers to their children, and the hearts of the children to their fathers.",
          {
            "noteId": 3611
          },
          "Otherwise, I will come and strike the land with a curse.”"
        ]
      }
    ],
    "footnotes": [
      {
        "noteId": 3608,
        "caller": "+",
        "text": "Or the Sun of Righteousness will rise with healing in His wings",
